'''''Kwaku Ananse'''''  ni film ngufi ya 2013 iyobowe na Akosua Adoma Owusu<ref>https://www.kweli.tv/programs/kwaku-ananse?locale=en</ref> . Filime ngufi ikomatanya ibintu byigice cya autobiographical hamwe numugani wa Kwaku Ananse, umunyamayeri mu nkuru zo muri [[Afrika]] yuburengerazuba na Karayibe bigaragara nkigitagangurirwa numugabo<ref>https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/kwaku-ananse-film</ref>. Umugani wa Kwaku Ananse uhujwe ninkuru y'umusore wo hanze witwa Nyan Koronhwea, witabiriye gushyingura se<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/kwaku-ananse/</ref>. Mu gihe cyo gushyingura, yasubiye mu ishyamba ashakisha se. Iyi filime yakinnye n'umucuranzi w'icyamamare Koo Nimo n'umukinnyi w'amafirime w'inararibonye Grace Omaboe<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/en/film411949.html</ref> . 

Amashusho yanditswe hamwe n’umukinnyi wa firime wo muri Pakisitani n’umunyamerika akaba na rwiyemezamirimo Iram Parveen Bilal<ref>https://www.indiewire.com/2015/06/interview-akosua-adoma-owusus-kwaku-ananse-at-the-institute-of-contemporary-art-philadelphia-153842/</ref> . Iyi nyandiko yandikiwe MaameYaa Boafo, umunyamerika wavukiye muri Pakisitani wavukiye muri [[Gana]], wahoze ari umukinnyi wa mbere nka Nyan Koronhwea<ref>https://www.timeout.com/accra/film/film-kwaku-ananse</ref>. Ariko, itsinda ryababyaye mumujyi wa New York amaherezo ryafashe umwanzuro wo gusubiramo imico mugihe cyabanjirije umusaruro hamwe na Jojo Abot, umuhanzi ukomoka muri [[Gana]]<ref>https://www.gubaawards.co.uk/2013/02/akosua-adoma-owusu-tells-a-modern-day-kwaku-ananse-story/</ref>.  

== Inyandiko ==
Dushingiye ku migani ikungahaye yo muri [[Gana]], iyi filime ngufi y’ubumaji ihuza ibintu byanditswe mu buzima bwa Owusu n’imigenzo ya rubanda kugira ngo ivuga amateka y’umukobwa ukiri muto w’umunyamerika wagarutse muri [[Afurika]] y’iburengerazuba gushyingura se, ariko akavumbura umwirondoro we wihishe kabiri<ref>http://www.africine.org/film/kwaku-ananse/14691</ref>.

Kwaku Ananse ni umugani gakondo wo muri [[Afrika]] y'uburengerazuba kubyerekeye ikiremwa kigizwe numuntu nigitagangurirwa, kimara imyaka ikusanya ubwenge bwose bwisi mumasafuriya y'imbaho. Mugihe agerageza guhisha inkono mugiti, ntashobora kubona uburyo bwo kuyishyira hejuru mumashami yacyo<ref>https://www.artforum.com/picks/akosua-adoma-owusu-56161</ref>. Iyo umuhungu we muto, Ntikuma amweretse inzira, Kwaku Ananse ararakara cyane, ajugunya inkono hasi. Iraturika kandi ubwenge burashira. Umuntu wese arihuta, yizeye gukiza ibyo ashoboye<ref>https://www.tabakalera.eus/en/akosua-adoma-owusu-0</ref>.

Nyan Koronhwea asubira kwa se Kwaku Ananse wavukiye muri [[Gana]] kumuhamba. Bari barabuze umubano hagati yabo kera. Yatandukanye ibyiyumvo by'ubuzima bwa se n'umuryango umwe muri [[Gana]] undi muri [[Amerika]]. Yarengewe n’ishyingurwa, asubira mu isi y’umwuka ashakisha Kwaku Ananse<ref>https://alchetron.com/Kwaku-Ananse-(film)</ref>.  

== Ibihembo ==
''Kwaku Ananse'' yatorewe kuba Golden Bear mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Berlin kandi yegukana igihembo cyiza cya Filime ngufi mu bihembo bya 9 bya Afurika Movie Academy Academy Awards .    Iyi filime kandi yakiriye abacamanza badasanzwe mu Ishyirahamwe Cinémas et Cultures d'Afrique 2015 i Angers, mu Bufaransa<ref>https://freshartinternational.com/2016/01/29/fresh-talk-akosua-adoma-owusu/</ref>.

